6. Conclusion

This project demonstrates the implementation of a secure and scalable cloud architecture using Azure services. By separating application and database layers into different subnets and using NAT Gateway and NSGs, the solution ensures enhanced security and controlled access.

The architecture follows real-world enterprise practices and can be extended further with load balancing, autoscaling, and monitoring solutions.

